Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory1249.jpg'}
{1: 'DialogDisable'}
{1: 'Babel Tower, 39th Floor'}
{3: 'Babel Tower, 39th Floor.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Dante', 3: "Alright, one more minute. If they don't show up, we're going up without them.", 4: '1'}
{3: "Dante and Vergil stand idly on the Babel Tower's 39th floor, boredom evident in their postures."}
{2: 'Dante', 3: 'So, who is she?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Dante', 3: "Oh c'mon, you know who. That woman, Nero's mom.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Dante', 3: "Seriously, I'm dying to know what kind of woman could've won Vergil's heart.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Dante', 3: 'Next time we see Nero, we should have a little dinner together. You know, a family dinner. Heh!', 4: '1'}
{3: "In response to Dante's question, Vergil simply rolls his eyes."}
{2: 'Vergil', 3: "You're hardly one to ask. What of the women around you? Have you given thought to their fates?", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Dante', 3: '...I take back my question.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Another moment of silence falls between them.'}
{3: 'Footsteps echo as you and Alpha appear by the door.'}
{2: "I've collected all the data.", 3: '37'}
{2: 'Dante', 3: "Nice work. Don't wreck it though. We'll need that for our return.", 4: '1'}
{1: 'DialogDisable'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory1248.jpg'}
{3: "The 39th floor of Babel Tower is different from the ones before. There aren't many doors, just a long staircase stretching out into the open."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Alpha', 3: 'Next up is the 40th floor.', 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStory/FxUiStoryBlackPassScene.prefab', 2: '2'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory1251.jpg'}
{3: 'You all move forward cautiously. Ahead of you stands the emaciated figure of Thomas, waiting in silence.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Dante', 3: "Looks like we've made it to the top.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Thomas Hell?', 3: "It's a pity that this tower only has 40 floors now. If I had just bided my time a bit longer, handling you all would have been much easier...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Dante', 3: 'Hmph, your little games end here.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Thomas Hell?', 3: 'Games? You dare call it games?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Vergil', 3: 'Hardly worthy of being called games... just the futile thrashing of a pest.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Thomas Hell?', 3: 'Oh, let me see... the blue big brother... hee... haha...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Thomas Hell?', 3: 'Shamefully defeated by the Demon Emperor Mundus...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Thomas Hell?', 3: 'And the red little brother, cowering in the Human World after the fire... playing house with his precious humans... hee...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Dante', 3: "Alright, now you've pissed me off. You better be ready for what's coming.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Thomas Hell?', 3: 'No, no, no. Before that, you\'ll have to face another entity... a "mirror image" first.', 4: '3'}
